        "content": "AI in healthcare can help detect heart disease, diagnose lung cancer more accurately, predict disease progression, and personalize cancer and surgical treatment. AI applications can analyze complex data to support doctors with treatment decisions and manage hospital bed demand. Examples include smart stethoscopes for heart failure detection and AI-assisted blood tests for heart attack diagnosis."
